{"title":"算是说明一样的东西","slug":"20190720","date":"2019-07-20T09:37:09.000Z","updated":"2019-07-22T02:44:52.102Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<p>昨天刚刚上完AQM，所以暑假的任务就剩下科研了。可能还有学英语？至今科研的进度很不妙。<br>\n蘑菇讨厌夏天，这个暑假发生了好多事情，可能还会发生一些事情——至少，昨天和前天对我而言大概发生了两个噩耗，之前的一个月内两次打击刚刚缓过来。<br>\n好消息是，工作变得单一了。虽然周一和周三还要看医生，但总归是单一的工作了，时间表也可以调回去了。可以集中精力了来着。以后也会把一些笔记贴上来。<br>\n哎——总之还是做吧？<br>\n另注：头像是跟着QQ头像走的。新头像是Arcaea收录曲Vindication的曲绘。<br>\n原图来自Arcaea 2.2.0的剧情，画师是Cierra老师。<br>\n另外希望大家能给2019.7.18京都动画纵火案的被害者捐款——侧边栏有链接，我也捐了一点。</p>\n<p>灰白的代码参照<a href=\"http://www.divcss5.com/wenji/w484.shtml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">链接</a>，在head里面添加。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- GREY--&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\">    html &#123; </span><br><span class=\"line\">        -webkit-filter: grayscale(100%); </span><br><span class=\"line\">        -moz-filter: grayscale(100%); </span><br><span class=\"line\">        -ms-filter: grayscale(100%); </span><br><span class=\"line\">        -o-filter: grayscale(100%); </span><br><span class=\"line\">        filter:progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.BasicImage(grayscale=1);  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">        _<span class=\"selector-tag\">filter</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:none</span>; </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<spa